videos.headline: Florida, FSU players have to be separated before game
videos.description: Florida and Florida State players nearly break out into a scuffle on the field prior to their heated rivalry match.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida, FSU players have to be separated before game) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kemore Gamble fights to keep his footing before reaching the end zone
videos.description: Kemore Gamble sheds a defender and keeps his footing on his way to a 47-yard Gators touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kemore Gamble scores 47-yard Receiving touchdown vs. Florida State) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Florida's defense comes away with a big INT
videos.description: Gino English's pass is intercepted by Rashad Torrence II to give the Gators great field position.

videos.headline: Florida's trick play fails as FSU comes away with INT
videos.description: A play after intercepting Florida State, Florida's trick play falls into the hands of Seminoles DB Jammie Robinson for an interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jammie Robinson makes timely pick vs. Florida State) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan Travis keeps it himself to put FSU on the board
videos.description: Jordan Travis calls his own number and keeps it for a 9-yard Seminoles touchdown.

videos.headline: FSU's defense comes up with its 3rd INT of the 1st half
videos.description: Jarvis Brownlee Jr. steps in front of the receiver to come away with Florida State's third interception vs. Florida.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Picked! Florida State throws pick in the 2nd quarter) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Justin Shorter makes a juggling circus catch for a Gators TD
videos.description: Justin Shorter bobbles the ball in midair before finally taking control in the back of the end zone for a Florida touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Justin Shorter scores 5-yard Receiving touchdown vs. Florida State) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dameon Pierce walks into the end zone untouched
videos.description: Dameon Pierce finds pay dirt on a 3-yard rushing touchdown to extend the Gators' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (End Zone! Dameon Pierce scores 3-yard Rushing TD vs. Florida State) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Treshaun Ward's rushing TD pulls Seminoles within 10
videos.description: Treshaun Ward takes the halfback draw to the house, pulling the Seminoles within 10 points.

videos.headline: Ontaria Wilson's acrobatic receiving TD pulls FSU within 4
videos.description: Ontaria Wilson makes an acrobatic, touchdown catch to pull the Seminoles within four points late in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jordan Travis airs it out for 8-yard touchdown Pass) 2021/11/27 ESHEET

videos.headline: Florida holds off Florida State
videos.description: Florida holds off Florida State to win its sixth game of the season.
